<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Thank You for Subscribing</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #f97316;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #f99750;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .unsubscribe {
            color: white;
        }

        .unsubscribe:hover {
            color: #f99650;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Thank You for Subscribing!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are excited to have you with us. Stay tuned for the latest updates, news, and exclusive offers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>You can always unsubscribe if you no longer wish to receive our emails. Click the button below to
                unsubscribe:</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" class="button unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a>
            </div>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>University</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>